    have h5 : eLpNorm (T' gÔéä) 1 (╬Ż.restrict G) ÔëĄ (c / p) * eLorentzNorm gÔéä p 1 ╬╝ * (╬Ż G) ^ p'Ôü╗┬╣.toReal := by
